ngirungiru
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the South Island tomtit. Compare MIROMIRO. [Maori] Williams 233 <i>Ngirungiru ... Petroica toitoi, white-breasted tit</i> (North Island), and <i>P. macrocephala macrocephala, yellow-breasted tit</i> (South Island). = <i>miromiro</i> ...: spg also <i>ngidu ngidu, ngiru-ngiru </i>erron. <i>ngoru-ngoru</i> cf also MIROMIRO, PIRANGIRANGI : ? white breasted ? or yellow-breasted SI tit
Origin:
